doctype
html
    head
        title Actano - Absentees
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='/styles.css')
    body
        h1 Actano - Absentees
        p List of teams and its members, <span class="absent">grayed out</span> members are not <a href="#hint">available</a> today.
        ul
            for result in results
                li
                    h2=result.name
                    ul
                        for member in result.members
                            - styleClass = ''
                            - if (result.absentees.indexOf(member) != -1) {styleClass='absent'}
                            li(class=styleClass)=member
        P(id='hint')
            small (available) can be with clients, on paid or sick leave, university, you name it.
